      "date": "2013-06-07 17:55:03.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThis build issue looks related to your patch. \n\n/var/lib/jenkins/workspace/lustre-reviews/arch/x86_64/build_type/server/distro/el6/ib_stack/ofa/BUILD/BUILD/lustre-2.4.50/lustre/osc/osc_io.c: In function 'osc_io_submit':\n/var/lib/jenkins/workspace/lustre-reviews/arch/x86_64/build_type/server/distro/el6/ib_stack/ofa/BUILD/BUILD/lustre-2.4.50/lustre/osc/osc_io.c:129: error: 'oap' undeclared (first use in this function)",
