          "date": "2013-09-05 20:37:58.000000000",
          "tz": 0
        },
        "subject": "LU-2744 build: fix race issues thanks to oap_lock",
        "message": "LU-2744 build: fix race issues thanks to oap_lock\n\nFix 'data race condition' defects found by Coverity version\n6.5.0:\nData race condition (MISSING_LOCK)\nAccessing variable without holding lock. Elsewhere,\nthis variable is accessed with lock held.\n\nThis patch is dedicated to code fragments involving oap_lock.\n\nSigned-off-by: Sebastien Buisson <sebastien.buisson@bull.net>\nChange-Id: Ibfd5fe6338c624a1ab98b83ec621bcd88d736491\nReviewed-on: http://review.whamcloud.com/6572\nTested-by: Hudson\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <whamcloud.maloo@gmail.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
